buddhichya uprokta kshamta vikasit karun antrik adhyayan prakriy nirdosh karnyasathi darsnik tatvanche aloadan karun sanshodhikarine ek mahina samayavadicha abhyaskram tayar kela jo shravana, pramanyukta manan, anuwad yane yukta hota.
